{"tid":1178333,"cid":17,"subCid":0,"title":"點解日本人咁崇夏威夷？","createTime":"2019-05-30T10:32:51.000Z","updateTime":"2019-06-01T12:47:44.000Z","uid":66351,"like":20,"dislike":4,"uniUserReply":25,"replies":[{"pid":"2245366463aeeced41ccefcc688e71cfbf7e72a5","tid":1178333,"uid":66351,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-05-30T10:32:51.000Z","msg":"成日見日本人旅遊勝地都係去夏威夷<img src=\"/assets/faces/lomoji/26.png\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><br />\n<br />\n例如 <br />\n求婚大作戰 去沙灘係去 夏威夷<br />\n日版五十次初吻又係 夏威夷<br />\n<br />\n連藍白航空最近都不停推廣飛夏威夷的廣告<br />\n<br />\n到底夏威夷有咩吸引 令佢地情願東飛都唔西飛？<img src=\"/assets/faces/dog/scare.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><br />\n<br />\n崇美的話 點解唔再遠少少 去東西岸呢<br />\n而話近的話 點解唔去港韓台呢？"},{"pid":"1630c39ac700dd52cbf34415a186a56def716176","tid":1178333,"uid":21225,"like":8,"dislike":0,"score":8,"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2019-05-30T10:36:08.000Z","msg":"陽光海灘 異國文化"},{"pid":"7f6c02baf212efefa733ea43ff11f492e41e7d90","tid":1178333,"uid":185884,"like":35,"dislike":1,"score":34,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-05-30T10:36:48.000Z","msg":"因為，近。"},{"pid":"57b12119b43605f333bc72c6b319b1d6c2926761","tid":1178333,"uid":191815,"like":3,"dislike":17,"score":-14,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-05-30T10:36:49.000Z","msg":"陽光與海灘 香港同夏威夷有得比<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/sosad.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/wonder2.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"e216c1d757aae9a0f6f2565758d0c339238fe4fc","tid":1178333,"uid":24339,"like":24,"dislike":0,"score":24,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-05-30T10:37:30.000Z","msg":"小新一家成日去<img src=\"/assets/faces/lm2/sosad.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"e8f9582ed84a29ff55caa25213c7f70b2fcbd807","tid":1178333,"uid":21225,"like":12,"dislike":0,"score":12,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-05-30T10:40:03.000Z","msg":"多人到飛A380"},{"pid":"8d1f709e8f9ab4ad1c7e7b20067f1e6ce1cf6f31","tid":1178333,"uid":199162,"like":8,"dislike":0,"score":8,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-05-30T10:45:55.000Z","msg":"好多跑手鍾意去跑馬拉松 因為手續簡單過日本好多"},{"pid":"9699b9ba80cd8d6